    General Stores in Chembur, Mumbai

    General Stores in Chembur, Mumbai

    General stores or mom-n-pop shops are known as 'kiranas' in most parts of the country. It is a form of traditional retail where it offers a wide range of products. As general stores, these establishments store items categorised as food grains, pulses, household items, toiletries, cosmetics, biscuits and packaged food items, bakery products, confectionery items, and local foods. Any of these stores house a vast variety of products ranging from loose grains and pulses to cosmetics. A modern general store may have air-conditioning, a wider range of products and services that local shops may not offer. Following the traditional system, most serve customers through a counter system, certain stores encourage self-service for their customers, by following a more modern system. Aiming for the convenience of the locals, these general stores also offer complimentary doorstep delivery services. Please scroll up to find a list of General Stores in Chembur, Mumbai.
